data.title: US trade agreement: MEPs meeting with a delegation of film director and extracts from the dialogue with MEPs
data.meta_description: A meeting on the defense of the cultural exception in the EU-US trade agreement takes place in the EP in Strasbourg, with the participatin of Henri WEBER (S&D, FR), Bérénice BEJO, French actress, Costa GAVRAS, film director, Lucas BELVAUX, Belgian actor and film director, Daniele LUCCHETTI, Italian actor and film director, Cristian MUNGIU, Romanian filmaker, and Radu MIHAILEANU, Romanian actor and film director,
data.text: Defending Cultural exception in the EU-US trade agreement: MEPs meeting with a delegation of film director and extracts from the dialogue with MEPs
